<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Projects</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/style.css"/>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Christopher Donnelly</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/projects">Projects <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
        @{
            string title = "Projects";
            <h1 class="pl-3 pr-3 pt-3">@title</h1>
        }
        <div class="col pt-4 pl-2 pr-2 text-center">
            <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide text-center" data-ride="carousel">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class=""></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2" class="active"></li>
                </ol>
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" alt="Samsara: Wandering Worlds" src="~/images/Samsara.png" data-holder-rendered="true">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block transbox">
                    <h5>Samsara: Wandering Worlds - Python Online Two Player Game</h5>
                    <p>Simple Tower Defense type game, buildings are of 5 different types (Earth, Fire, Water, Metal and Wood) which produce Units of the same type.  The Units move toward the enemy, attacking other Units and buildings along the way in a Rock, Paper, Scisscors, Lizard, Spock style battle system. If the Unit survives the battles or is unobstructed it will deal damage to the Enemy player.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" alt="Tetris Madness" src="~/images/TetrisMadness.png" data-holder-rendered="true">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block transbox">
                    <h5>Tetris Madness - MEAN Online Two Player Game</h5>
                    <p>Two player online Battle Tetris game.  Clearing 2 or more lines will send concrete blocks to the opponent. Levels increase fast which increases the seed of the game creating fast paced enjoyable Tetris experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" alt="Brave Rat" src="~/images/BraveRat.png" data-holder-rendered="true">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block transbox">
                    <h5>Brave Rat - C# Two Player Local Console Game</h5>
                    <p>A Blue Orange<sup>&COPY;</sup> card game original game idea by Seiji Kanai.  This project was created as a single day Hackathon project for C# Console application.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="~/js/bootstrap.min.js" ></script>
    <script>
        $('.carousel').carousel({
            interval: 5000
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>